dBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"係咩？我覺得會明一部分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"要你聽潮州話,客家,&nbsp;雷洲,&nbsp;你聽得明咩?<br />\n<br />\n純香港人去珠海,&nbsp;廣州,&nbsp;江門,&nbsp;同湛江會好易溝通到<br />\n去肇慶,&nbsp;佛山,&nbsp;陽光,惠洲 都應該聽明大部分生存到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"潮州話其實應該係閩語閩南話嘅分支<br />\n只係因為靠近廣東所以先帶有少量粵語特色<br />\n<br />\n至於梅州客家話, 係客語, 都唔係粵語<br />\n<br />\n至於雷州, 靠近海南島, 發音似瓊海話, 又係閩南話嘅分支, 夾雜多啲粵語特色咁解<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff14824cd071ad8c3443819e117fc06cb9672859","tid":2418953,"uid":329733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fc3c30b8fd6de5b09e029d7f64fbe95c4c00c55","tid":2418953,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"3c49d27a44ecc575af8c77ca9a39b7d902dfaff6","tid":2418953,"uid":223428,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T06:54:59.000Z","msg":"瑞士：呃&hellip;&hellip;<del>(我唔團結咩)</del>保持中立"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"本身想講若果瑞士好窮乜乜乜<br />\n然後醒起瑞士本身真係好窮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:16:37.000Z","msg":"瑞士窮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講乜嘢？？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa